---
description: "JS/TS style: no semicolons, single quotes, oxlint + oxfmt enforced"
alwaysApply: true
---

- No semicolons in TypeScript/JavaScript
- Single quotes for strings; JSX attributes use double quotes
- `printWidth: 100`, `tabWidth: 2`, trailing commas everywhere
- Formatting via `mise run format:fix`; linting via `mise run lint`
- `no-explicit-any: warn` — use `unknown` for untyped input, then narrow
- `consistent-type-imports: error` — use `import type` for type-only imports
- `import/no-cycle: error` — no circular dependencies
